---
layout: base.njk
title: Bible Explorer
description: Chapter-by-chapter summaries, organized by sections and books.
---

<div class="header">
  <h1>Bible Explorer</h1>
  <p class="meta">Explore the Bible with chapter-by-chapter summaries, Bible Project videos, and commentary links.</p>
</div>

<div class="chapter-summary">
  <h3>Features</h3>
  <ul style="color: var(--text); line-height: 1.8;">
    <li><strong>Detailed Chapter Summaries:</strong> Concise, in-depth summaries for every chapter</li>
    <li><strong>Bible Project Videos:</strong> Embedded overview videos for each book</li>
    <li><strong>Commentary Links:</strong> Direct access to Enduring Word commentary</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile-Friendly:</strong> Optimized for reading on any device</li>
    <li><strong>Organized Structure:</strong> Browse by biblical categories and themes</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2>Biblical Sections</h2>
<div class="grid">
  {% for sec in categories %}
    <a class="card" href="/categories/{{ sec.slug }}/">
      <h3>{{ sec.name }}</h3>
      <p>{{ sec.description }}</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 0.8rem;">
        {% if sec.bookCount %}
          <span class="badge" style="background: rgba(106, 169, 255, 0.1); color: var(--accent);">{{ sec.bookCount }} books</span>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="badge">{{ sec.testament }}</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top:2rem;">All Books ({{ books | length }})</h2>
<div class="grid">
  {% for b in books %}
    <a class="card" href="/books/{{ b.slug }}/">
      <h3>{{ b.name }}</h3>
      <p><strong>{{ b.author }}</strong> • {{ b.category }}</p>
      {% if b.chapterSummaries and (b.chapterSummaries | length) > 0 %}
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          ✓ {{ b.chapterSummaries | length }} chapters with summaries
        </p>
      {% endif %}
      <span class="badge">{{ b.testament }}</span>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
